5C%22%3EAmazon%3C%2Fa%3E%20CFO%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-starbucks-earnings-how-cautious-us-consumers-spending-sales-decline-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBrian%20Olsavsky%3C%2Fa%3E%20says%20the%20volatile%20news%20cycle%20is%20partly%20to%20blame%20for%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-prices-rising-shoppers-cautious-economy-outlook-earnings-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elower%20than%20expected%20sales%20forecast%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20quarter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Thursday%2C%20the%20e-commerce%20giant%20said%20it%20was%20expecting%20%24154%20billion%20to%20%24158.5%20billion%20in%20revenue%20for%20the%20third%20quarter%20of%20this%20year%2C%20below%20the%20average%20analyst%20estimate%20of%20%24158.24%20billion.%20Amazon%20stock%20prices%20fell%20by%20more%20than%207%25%20in%20after-hours%20trading.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20the%20revenue%20side%2C%20I'd%20just%20say%20it's%20going%20to%20be%20a%20tough%20quarter%20to%20forecast%2C%26quot%3B%20Amazon%20CFO%20Brian%20Olsavsky%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Fbusiness%2Fearnings%2Famazon-amzn-q2-earnings-report-2024-8665256b%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Wall%20Street%20Journal's%20Sebastian%20Herrera%3C%2Fa%3E%20during%20a%20press%20briefing%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20lot%20of%20events%20that%20are%20occupying%20people's%20attention%20right%20now%20from%20political%20conventions%20to%20the%20election%20itself%20to%20the%20Olympics%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOlsavsky%20later%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.axios.com%2F2024%2F08%2F01%2Famazon-stock-earnings-consumer-spending%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAxios'%20Hope%20King%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20same%20briefing%20that%20the%20spate%20of%20newsmaking%20events%20in%20the%20recent%20and%20coming%20months%20meant%20that%20it%20would%20be%20much%20harder%20for%20Amazon%20to%20sell%20to%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%20matter%20what%20you're%20selling%20or%20providing%2C%20customers%20only%20have%20so%20much%20attention%2C%26quot%3B%20Olsavsky%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20high%20profile%20things%20happen%2C%20or%20the%20assassination%20attempt%20a%20couple%20of%20weeks%20ago%2C%20you%20do%20see%20that%20people%20shift%20their%20attention%20to%20news%2C%20and%20so%20it's%20more%20about%20distractions%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20continued%2C%20referencing%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdonald-trump-butler-pennsylvania-rally-secret-service-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efailed%20attempt%20on%20former%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20life%3C%2Fa%3E%20during%20a%20Pennsylvania%20rally%20last%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20times%20purchases%20will%20defer%2C%20and%20people%20will%20come%20back%20and%20buy%20what%20they%20were%20going%20to%20buy%2C%20and%20other%20times%20that%20won't%20happen%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20be%20sure%2C%20dealing%20with%20a%20wild%20news%20cycle%20isn't%20the%20only%20problem%20on%20Amazon's%20plate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20issuing%20a%20weak%20revenue%20forecast%2C%20the%20company%20also%20said%20it%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-stock-amzn-quarterly-earnings-call-report-live-updates-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emissed%20sales%20estimates%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20second%20quarter%20of%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Olsavsky%2C%20the%20dip%20in%20sales%20was%20driven%20by%20a%20shift%20in%20consumer%20behavior%2C%20with%20people%20opting%20to%20be%20more%20frugal%20with%20their%20spending.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20seeing%20cautious%20consumers%2C%20they're%20looking%20for%20deals%2C%20they're%20trading%20down%20to%20lower%20ASP%20(average%20sales%20price)%20options%20when%20they%20can%2C%20and%20that%20hasn't%20changed%2C%26quot%3B%20Olsavsky%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20shift%20resulted%20in%20brisk%20sales%20for%20Amazon's%20lower-priced%20Everyday%20Essentials%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20far%20us%2C%20the%20volume%20of%20units%20sold%20actually%20accelerated%20slightly%20when%20you%20adjust%20for%20the%20leap%20year%20effect%20in%20Q1%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20just%20right%20now%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20traction%20is%20to%20lower%20ASP%20products%20and%20that%20is%20impacting%20the%20revenue%20growth%20a%20bit.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-cfo-blames-olympics-and-trump-assassination-for-slowing-sales-2024-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722570478000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66ac4037393cd3c8629acc2d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-cfo-blames-olympics-and-trump-assassination-for-slowing-sales-2024-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Brian%20Olsavsky%20told%20reporters%20that%20Amazon%20customers%20were%20being%20distracted%20by%20the%20Olympics%20and%20the%20presidential%20elections.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ktan%40businessinsider.com%20(Kwan%20Wei%20Kevin%20Tan)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-cfo-blames-olympics-and-trump-assassination-for-slowing-sales-2024-8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22No%20pre-planned%20plot%20in%20Atiq%20Ahmed%20killing%3A%20UP%20judicial%20panel%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722570323000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-112212117%2Cimgsize-42730.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Flucknow%2Fno-pre-planned-plot-in-gangster-atiq-ahmed-killing-up-judicial-panel%2Farticle