%22%3EApparently%2C%202%20in%201%20didn't%20like%20my%20Chakravyuh%20speech.%20ED%20%E2%80%98insiders'%20tell%20me%20a%20raid%20is%20being%20planned.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnWaiting%20with%20open%20arms%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdir_ed%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40dir_ed%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%A6..Chai%20and%20biscuits%20on%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20(%40RahulGandhi)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FRahulGandhi%2Fstatus%2F1819106372396765206%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EAugust%201%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20comes%20after%20Mr%20Gandhi%20attacked%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20while%20speaking%20on%20the%20Union%20Budget%202024%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20on%20July%2029.%20He%20said%20farmers%2C%20workers%2C%20and%20youngsters%20of%20the%20nation%20are%20terrified.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20criticised%20PM%20Modi%20for%20prominently%20displaying%20the%20lotus%20symbol%20and%20claimed%20that%20a%20new%20'Chakravyuh'%20had%20been%20created%20in%20the%2021st%20century.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThousands%20of%20years%20ago%2C%20in%20Kurukshetra%2C%20six%20people%20trapped%20Abhimanyu%20in%20a%20'Chakravyuh'%20and%20killed%20him.%20I%20did%20a%20little%20research%20and%20found%20out%20that%20'Chakravyuh'%20is%20also%20known%20as%20'Padmavuyh'%20-%20which%20means%20'Lotus%20formation'.%20Chakravyuh'%20is%20in%20the%20shape%20of%20a%20Lotus.%20In%20the%2021st%20century%2C%20a%20new%20'Chakravyuh'%20has%20been%20formed%20-%20that%20too%20in%20the%20form%20of%20a%20Lotus.%20The%20Prime%20Minister%20wears%20its%20symbol%20on%20his%20chest.%20What%20was%20done%20with%20Abhimanyu%2C%20is%20being%20down%20with%20India%20-%20the%20youth%2C%20farmers%2C%20women%2C%20small%20and%20medium%20businesses.%20Abhimanyu%20was%20killed%20by%20six%20people.%20Today%2C%20too%20there%20are%20six%20people%20in%20the%20centre%20of%20'Chakravyuh'.%20Six%20people%20control%20India%20today%20t