09%20close%20in%20the%20first%20game%20but%20unending%20unforced%20errors%20meant%20that%20Bing%20Jao%20ran%20away%20with%20the%20match%2021-19%2021-14%20in%2056%20minutes.%20Sindhu%20even%20dictated%20a%20few%20points%20but%20had%20no%20answer%20to%20Bing%20Jiao's%20superior%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20should%20have%20controlled%20in%20terms%20of%20a%20little%20bit%20of%20mistakes%20on%20my%20defense%20is%20what%20I%20felt%2C%26quot%3B%20Sindhu%20said%2C%20reflecting%20upon%20the%20reason%20for%20her%20defeat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESindhu%20had%20a%20training%20camp%20in%20Germany%20and%20also%20joined%20forces%20with%20mentor%20Prakash%20Padukone%20for%20better%20preparation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEverybody%20worked%20hard%2C%20so%20we've%20done%20whatever%20we%20could.%20Rest%20is%20destiny.%20I%20don't%20regret%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20kept%20fighting%20still%20because%20you%20never%20know%20anything%20can%20happen.%20Both%20of%20us%20were%20fighting%20for%20each%20point%20because%20until%20the%20end%20you%20can't%20expect.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20easy%20win%20or%20easy%20points%2C%20you%20can't%20think%20that%20you%20have%20finished%20the%20game.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBing%20Jiao's%20smashes%20and%20soft%20drops%20had%20Sindhu%20scurrying%20on%20both%20sides%20of%20the%20court.%20But%20when%20Sindhu%20attacked%2C%20the%20Chinese%20defended%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20has%20that%20jump%20smash.%20Even%20my%20smashes%2C%20I%20think%2C%20which%20were%20mid-court%2C%20they%20were%20just%20going%20out%20when%20she%20was%20challenging.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20should%20have%20hit%20them%20inside%20and%20I%20should%20have%20got%20those%20points%20where%20I've%20made%20those%20unforced%20errors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20got%20much%20more%20confident%20in%20that%20because%20when%20I%20was%20hitting%2C%20she%20was%20defending%2C%20but%20stil