0for%20one%2C%20makes%20it%20extremely%20difficult%20to%20align%20supply%20with%20demand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20companies%20that%20want%20to%20meet%20a%20sudden%20uptick%20in%20demand%20must%20make%20hefty%20investments%20to%20boost%20production.%20While%20this%20would%20certainly%20raise%20supply%20levels%2C%20it%20also%20risks%20creating%20an%20oversupply%20if%20demand%20dies%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20means%20that%20investors%20could%20be%20left%20hanging%20if%20they%20time%20the%20semiconductor%20supercycle%20wrongly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20now%2C%20the%20chip%20industry%20has%20found%20itself%20buoyed%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-much-big-tech-spending-on-ai-investments-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esurge%20in%20funding%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20AI-related%20investments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20has%20resulted%20in%20a%20big%20payday%20for%20Nvidia%2C%20which%20has%20done%20brisk%20business%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-mark-zuckerberg-ai-chips-gpus-meta-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMeta's%20Mark%20Zuckerberg%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-ceo-elon-musk%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETesla's%20Elon%20Musk%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZuckerberg%20even%20touted%20Meta's%20growing%20stockpile%20of%20Nvidia%20chips%20in%20an%20interview%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F2024%2F1%2F18%2F24042354%2Fmark-zuckerberg-meta-agi-reorg-interview%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Verge%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20January%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20expects%20the%20company%20to%20own%20more%20than%20340%2C000%20Nvidia%20H100%20GPUs%20by%20the%20end%20of%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20some%20segments%20in%20the%20industry%20have%20already%20seen%20a%20slowdown%2C%20such%20as%20those%20relating%20to%20chips%20for%20consumer%20electronics.%20In%20April%2C%20chip%20manufacturer%20TSMC%20said%20it%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2024-04-18%2Ftsmc-posts-first-profit-growth-in-a-year-after-global-ai-boom%3Fsref%3DnfBouUGg%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elowering%20its%20growth%20forecasts%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20citing%20weak%20smartphone%20and%20personal%20computer%20sales.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20boom%20in%20data%20center%20builds%20has%20also%20spurred%20significant%20chip%20demand.%20If%20data%20center%20investment%20slows%2C%20chip%20firms%20could%20take%20a%20hit%2C%20Miller%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20be%20sure%2C%20not%20everyone%20thinks%20we%20are%20at%20the%20peak%20of%20the%20AI-driven%20supercycle%20just%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20rising%20demand%20for%20electricity%20due%20to%20digitalization%2C%20AI%2C%20and%20the%20use%20of%20renewable%20energies%20are%20increasing%20the%20demand%20for%20metal%20raw%20materials%2C%26quot%3B%20Thomas%20Rupf%2C%20chief%20investment%20officer%20at%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eprivate%20bank%20VP%20Bank%20in%20Asia%2C%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20still%20too%20early%20to%20declare%20a%20new%20super%20cycle%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20there%20are%20still%20investment%20opportunities%20in%20areas%20like%20industrial%20metals%20and%20mining%2C%20both%20boosted%20by%20AI%20demand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ey.com%2Fen_sg%2Fpeople%2Fjosie-ananto%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJosie%20Ananto%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20principal%20at%20EY-Parthenon's%20strategy%20and%20transactions%20team%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20the%20growing%20ubiquity%20of%20chips%20means%20that%20demand%20will%20be%20a%20lot%20more%20persistent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20growth%20of%20the%20semiconductor%20sector%20is%20not%20a%20hype%20%E2%80%94%20it%20is%20real%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BFor%20example%2C%20electric%20vehicles%20in%20the%20automotive%20sector%2C%20product%20innovation%20in%20l