20in%20rainwater%20that%20gushed%20into%20the%20basement%20of%20their%20house%20in%20the%20Vishwakarma%20area%20in%20Jaipur.%20After%20the%20water%20entered%20the%20basement%20of%20their%20houses%20at%20around%204%20am%2C%20the%20families%20began%20removing%20their%20belongings%2C%20Deputy%20Commissioner%20of%20Police%20(DCP)%20West%20Amit%20Kumar%20said.%20The%20passage%20to%20the%20basement%20of%20the%20house%20is%20narrow%20and%20deep.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20this%20time%2C%20three%20people%20from%20two%20families%20got%20trapped%20in%20the%20basement%20as%20it%20started%20filling%20with%20water%2C%20Kumar%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20a%20rescue%20operation%20was%20initiated%20and%20the%20rainwater%20was%20pumped%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bodies%20were%20recovered%20by%20the%20SDRF%20during%20a%20rescue%20operation%20that%20lasted%20several%20hours%2C%20the%20police%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExpressing%20condolences%20over%20the%20incident%2C%20CM%20Sharma%20directed%20officials%20to%20provide%20financial%20assistance%20of%20Rs%205%20lakh%20to%20the%20family%20of%20each%20deceased.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApproval%20to%20grant%20Rs%204%20lakh%20from%20disaster%20relief%20fund%20and%20Rs%201%20lakh%20from%20chief%20minister's%20relief%20fund%20has%20been%20given%2C%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeputy%20CM%20Diya%20Kumari%20visited%20the%20family%20members%20of%20the%20deceased%20and%20expressed%20condolences.%20She%20said%20that%20efforts%20have%20been%20made%20to%20address%20the%20problem%20of%20water%20logging%20in%20the%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20the%20residents%20of%20the%20area%20have%20been%20advised%20not%20to%20stay%20in%20their%20basements%20during%20rainfall%2C%20the%20police%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bodies%20of%20the%20victims%20have%20been%20shifted%20to%20Kanwatiya%20Government%20Hospital%20for%20postmortem%2C%20the%20police%20said%2C%20all%20the%20victims%20are%20native%20of%20Bihar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bodies%20were%20handed%20over%20after%20postmortem.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Jhalawar%2C%20three%20people%2C%20including%20a%20woman%2C%20riding%20on%20a%20motorcycle%20on%20a%20bridge%20were%20swept%20away%20by%20the%20overflowing%20Kalisindh%20river%20this%20afternoon%2C%20Mandawar%20SHO%20Mahaveer%20Prasad%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20have%20not%20been%20identified%20yet%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20search%20operation%20was%20launched%20but%20none%20of%20them%20could%20be%20traced%20till%20the%20evening%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Jaipur's%20Bagru%20area%2C%20a%2015-year%20old%20boy%2C%20identified%20as%20Piyush%20Acharya%2C%20was%20swept%20away%20in%20a%20drain.%20He%20was%20rescued%20and%20rushed%20to%20a%20nearby%20hospital%20where%20he%20died%2C%20the%20police%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDue%20to%20heavy%20rains%20that%20started%20on%20Wednesday%20night%2C%20most%20areas%20of%20Jaipur%20city%20were%20waterlogged%2C%20which%20continued%20till%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERainwater%20accumulated%20on%20roads%20and%20in%20residential%20areas%20in%20the%20state%20capital%2C%20causing%20significant%20commuting%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJaipur%20Collector%20Prakash%20Raj%20Purohit%20visited%20rain-affected%20areas%2C%20such%20as%20Vishwakarma%20area%2C%20Sikar%20Road%2C%20and%20directed%20officials%20to%20make%20necessary%20arrangements%20for%20the%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20schools%20in%20Jaipur%20declared%20a%20holiday%20due%20to%20the%20continued%20rainfall.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Churu%2C%20a%20nearly%20100-year-old%20building%20located%20at%20Bhai%20Ji%20Chowk%20collapsed%20due%20to%20heavy%20rains.%20However%2C%20no%20one%20was%20injured.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20heavy%20rains%20in%20Kota%2C%20a%20bus%20overturned%20and%20fell%20into%20a%2020%20feet%20deep%20ditch%2C%20leaving%20four%20passengers%20injured%20while%2031%20passengers%20were%20evacuated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHeavy%20rains%20in%20Phagi%20town%20of%20Dudu%20district%20flooded%20the%20roads.%20During%20this%2C%20a%20roadways%20bus%20full%20of%20passengers%20got%20stuck%20in%20the%20water.%20Local%20people%20pulled%20it%20out%20with%20a%20tractor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERainwater%20accumulated%20on%20roads%20and%20residential%20areas%20in%20many%20parts%20of%20the%20state%20capital%2C%20causing%20traffic%20to%20crawl.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPassengers%20faced%20trouble%20in%20entering%20the%20terminal%20in%20the%20early%20hours%20of%20the%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20CM%20Sharma%20took%20a%20meeting%20through%20video%20conference%20and%20directed%20officials%20to%20the%20field%20and%20take%20stock%20of%20the%20situation%20and%20ensure%20immediate%20relief%20to%20the%20public%20in%20case%20of%20disaster.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20instructed%20the%20officials%20to%20identify%20old%20and%20dilapidated%20buildings%20during%20the%20monsoon%20season%2C%20so%20that%20any%20kind%20of%20damage%20can%20be%20prevented%20in%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CM%20also%20asked%20the%20medical%20and%20health%20department%20officials%20to%20ensure%20adequate%20availability%20of%20medical%20facilities%20to%20prevent%20seasonal%20diseases%2C%20according%20a%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Jaipur%20Meteorological%20Centre%2C%20Jaipur%2C%20Karauli%2C%20Sawai%20Madhopur%2C%20Alwar%2C%20Churu%2C%20Bharatpur%2C%20Tonk%2C%20Sikar%2C%20Hanumangarh%2C%20Dholpur%2C%20Nagaur%20and%20Jhunjhunu%20recorded%20heavy%20to%20very%20heavy%20rainfall%20in%20a%20period%20of%2024%20hours%20till%208.30%20am%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJaipur%20recorded%20the%20highest%20rainfall%20of%20173%20mm%20during%20this%20period%2C%20the%20weather%20office%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20from%208.30%20am%20to%205.30%20pm%20on%20Thursday%2C%20Ganganagar%20recorded%20a%20maximum%20of%2048%20mm%20rains%20while%20several%20other%20areas%20recorded%20below%2048%20mm%20rains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20