ontent%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EMuch%20of%20the%20discourse%20around%20climate%20change%20tends%20to%20focus%20on%20technological%20%26quot%3Bmegafixes%26quot%3B%20and%20a%20renewable%20energy%20push%20may%20have%2C%20ironically%2C%20contributed%20to%20the%20landslides%20in%20Wayanad%20in%20which%20nearly%20300%20people%20have%20been%20killed%2C%20noted%20author%20and%20climate%20activist%20Amitav%20Ghosh%20has%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20exclusive%20interview%20with%20NDTV%20on%20Thursday%2C%20Mr%20Ghosh%20also%20said%20that%20there%20seems%20to%20be%20an%20inverse%20correlation%20between%20climate%20issues%20and%20people's%20attention%20to%20them%20because%20while%20one%20has%20been%20worsening%2C%20the%20other%20has%20been%20decreasing.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20the%20landslides%20in%20Kerala%2C%20one%20of%20the%20real%20problems%20over%20there%20is%20that%20there%20is%20just%20too%20much%20construction.%20This%20whole%20region%20has%20been%20so%20badly%20affected%20and%20this%20is%20not%20the%20first%20year...%20it's%20been%20going%20on%20for%20a%20very%20long%20time%2C%20going%20back%20to%202018.%20We%20see%20repeatedly%20the%20problems%20that%20arise%20from%20climate%20change%20affecting%20Uttarakhand%2C%20affecting%20Kerala%2C%20creating%20ever-greater%20impacts%2C%20and%20yet%20we%20don't%20seem%20to%20adapt%20at%20all%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20author%2C%20many%20of%20whose%20books%20speak%20of%20the%20devastating%20effects%20of%20climate%20change%2C%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20a%20question%20on%20the%20measures%20taken%20by%20India%20to%20combat%20climate%20change%20and%20what%20he%20thought%20of%20the%20green%20hydrogen%20push%2C%20Mr%20Ghosh%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20know%20the%20government%20has%20been%20talking%20up%20green%20hydrogen%2C%20but%20where%20do%20we%20see%20the%20results%3F%20Unfortunately%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20discourse%20around%20climate%20change%20tends%20to%20focus%20on%20technological%20megafixes%2C%20which%20actually%20never%20deliver.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20of%20the%20great%20ironies%20of%20climate%20change%20is%20that%20often%20the%20renewable%20energy%20mirage%20creates%20disasters%20in%20itself.%20In%20Wayanad%2C%20one%20of%20the%20problems%20is%20that%20people%20began%20to%20construct%20windmills%2C%20which%20is%20a%20good%20thing%2C%20I%20suppose%2C%20but%20to%20get%20to%20them%20you%20need%20roads%2C%20and%20roads%20destabilise%20the%20hillsides%2C%20leading%20to%20landslides.%20One%20of%20the%20major%20problems%20is%20road-building%3B%20it%20is%20a%20major%20problem%20in%20Uttarakhand%2C%20in%20the%20northeast%20and%20it%20is%20a%20major%20problem%20in%20Kerala.%20Wayanad%20is%20a%20major%20tourist%20region%20and%20the%20roads%20become%20heavily%20frequented%20and%20that%20leads%20to%20problems%20in%20itself%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20climate%20activist%20emphasised%20that%20climate%20change%20impacts%20are%20also%20often%20exacerbated%20by%20a%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%26quot%3Bmistaken%26quot%3B%20model%20of%20development%20in%20which%20there%20is%20building%20without%20proper%20oversight%20and%20without%20conducting%20studies%20of%20how%20the%20environment%20will%20be%20affected.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BForecasting%20methods%20give%20us%20a%20general%20picture%20of%20what%20might%20happen%2C%20they%20can't%20forecast%20localised%20defects%2C%20for%20which%20you%20have%20to%20look%20at%20local%20knowledge.%20Several%20people%20in%20Wayanad%20had%20the%20foresight%20to%20leave%20those%20areas%20before%20the%20landslides%20struck.%20Another%20thing%20I%20would%20like%20to%20emphasise%20is%20that%20we%20have%20been%20following%20this%20very%20technology%20oriented%20idea%20of%20development%2C%20and%20that%20in%20itself%20has%20been%20a%20large%20part%20of%20the%20problem.%20This%20part%20of%20Wayanad%20(where%20the%20landslides%20occurred)%20for%20example%2C%20is%20famous%20for%20its%20plantations.%20It%20has%20tea%20plantations.%20It%20has%20cardamom%20plantations%2C%20rubber%20plantations%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Ghosh%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20following%20an%20industrialised%20model%20of%20agriculture%20can%20create%20vulnerabilities%20and%20just%20having%20a%20green%20cover%20is%20not%20the%20same%20as%20forestation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20has%20happened%20in%20Wayanad%20was%20predicted%20years%20and%20years%20ago%20by%20Madhav%20Gadgil%2C%20the%20great%20environmentalist.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20Gadgil%20report%20recommended%20that%20this%20entire%20region%20be%20treated%20as%20an%20ecologically%20sensitive%20area%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Can't%20Absolve%20Themselves'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20climate%20change%20across%20the%20world%20and%20the%20steps%20that%20can%20be%20taken%20to%20mitigate%20it%2C%20Mr%20Ghosh%20said%20the%20developed%20world%20is%20responsible%2C%20for%20the%20most%20part%2C%20for%20greenhouse%20emissions%20but%20they%20are%20not%20willing%20to%20bear%20the%20burden.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20look%20at%20what%20the%20developed%20world%20is%20spending%20on%20climate%20mitigation%20and%20what%20it's%20spending%20on%20armaments%20right%20now%2C%20especially%20since%20the%20start%20of%20the%20Ukraine%20war%2C%20their%20defence%20spending%20is%20in%20multiples%20of%20hundreds%20more%20than%20their%20climate%20spending.%20Increasingly%2C%20there's%20a%20huge%20sort%20of%20backlash%20against%20any%20kind%20of%20climate%20measures.%20We%20see%20this%20in%20Europe%2C%20we%20see%20this%20in%20America.%20The%20Global%20South%20should%20continue%20to%20press%20very%20strongly%20for%20action%20from%20the%20developed%20world%20on%20climate%20change%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%2C%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%20it's%20incumbent%20on%20us.%20It's%20incumbent%20on%20all%20the%20governments%20of%20the%20Global%20South%20to%20also%20act%20to%20mitigate%20climate%20change%20impacts%20locally%20and%20regionally.%20This%20is%20a%20very%20important%20thing%20that%20we%20have%20to%20consider%2C%20we%20can't%20just%20blame%20climate%20change.%20This%20should%20not%20become%20a%20way%20for%20politicians%20and%20bureaucrats%20to%20absolve%20themselves%20of%20the%20responsibility%20for%20these%20impacts%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20author%20stressed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Not%20Much%20Has%20Changed'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEight%20years%20ago%2C%20Mr%20Ghosh%20had%20written%20that%20cultural%20failure%20is%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20the%20climate%20change%20crisis.%20When%20he%20was%20asked%20if%20he%20could%20see%20any%20change%20since%20then%2C%20he%20rued%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20to%20say%2C%20that's%20not%20the%20case%20at%20all.%20I%20think%20that%20more%20and%20more%20as%20climate%20issues%20worsen%2C%20people%20pay%20less%20and%20less%20attention%20to%20climate%20change.%20Especially%20culturally%2C%20we%20have%20not%20adapted%20at%20all.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722530760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fnehs27o8_amitav-ghosh_625x300_01_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Famitav-ghosh-wayanad-landslides-climate-change-in-wayanad-landslides-amitav-ghosh-points-to-renewable-energy-angle-6241673%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Much%20of%20the%20discourse%20around%20climate%20change%20tends%20to%20focus%20on%20technological%20%26quot%3Bmegafixes%26quot%3B%20and%20a%20renewable%20energy%20push%20may%20have%2C%20ironically%2C%20contributed%20to%20the%20landslides%20in%20Wayanad%2C%20author%20Amitav%20Ghosh%20has%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Famitav-ghosh-wayanad-landslides-climate-change-in-wayanad-landslides-amitav-ghosh-points-to-renewable-energy-angle-6241673%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com