lement-caption%5C%22%3EAtul%20Kulkarni%20is%20leading%20change%20from%20the%20front%20in%20the%20Dharashiv%20district%20of%20Osmanabad%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20anti-trafficking%20and%20theft%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Atul%20Kulkarni%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20a%20year%20since%20its%20inception%3B%20the%20impact%20has%20been%20telling.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20were%20around%20300%20families%20whose%20members%20were%20engaged%20in%20alcoholic%20and%20robbing%20activities.%20We%20rehabilitated%20them%20through%20this%20initiative.%20We%20have%20also%20ensured%20jobs%20for%20over%20500%20youth%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kulkarni%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20not%20for%20these%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F136884%2Fmumbai-school-dropouts-youth-employment-skill-training%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etraining%20programmes%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20he%20says%20you%E2%80%99d%20spot%20these%20youth%20at%20signals%20in%20metropolitan%20cities%2C%20where%20they%20otherwise%20engage%20in%20seasonal%20begging.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20around%2040%2C000%20people%20in%20the%20district%20living%20in%20hamlets.%20They%20do%20not%20even%20possess%20an%20Aadhaar%20Card%20or%20birth%20certificate%2C%20nor%20go%20to%20school%20or%20work.%20Their%20main%20income%20comes%20from%20robbing%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIs%20it%20easy%20to%20convince%20these%20people%20to%20change%20their%20mindsets%3F%20%E2%80%9CNo%2C%20but%20I%20go%20personally%20knocking%20on%20their%20doors%2C%E2%80%9D%20responds%20Kulkarni.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20quest%20to%20better%20people%E2%80%99s%20lives%20only%20grows%20with%20every%20passing%20day.%20And%20so%2C%20Parth%E2%80%99s%20newfound%20freedom%20is%20of%20special%20significance%20to%20Kulkarni%2C%20who%20is%20thrilled%20he%20was%20able%20to%20contribute%20to%20it.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20goes%20beyond%20duty.%20It%E2%80%99s%20an%20