20in%20the%20small%20Jhajjar%20district%20of%20Haryana%2C%20she%20initially%20dabbled%20in%20a%20variety%20of%20sports%20%E2%80%94%20from%20boxing%20and%20skating%20to%20tennis%20and%20martial%20arts.%20However%2C%20it%20was%20shooting%20where%20she%20found%20her%20true%20calling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20completed%20her%20schooling%20at%20Universal%20Public%20Secondary%20School%20and%20graduated%20with%20an%20honours%20degree%20in%20political%20science%20from%20Lady%20Shri%20Ram%20College%2C%20University%20of%20Delhi%2C%20in%202021.%20Currently%2C%20she%20is%20pursuing%20a%20degree%20in%20public%20administration%20at%20Punjab%20University.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F133458%2Fharyana-girl-makes-history-becomes-youngest-indian-win-shooting-world-cup%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHer%20talent%20in%20shooting%20became%20evident%20on%20the%20global%20stage%20in%202018%3C%2Fa%3E%20when%20she%20clinched%20multiple%20gold%20medals%20at%20the%20ISSF%20World%20Cup%2C%20becoming%20one%20of%20the%20youngest%20athletes%20to%20achieve%20such%20a%20feat.%20Her%20performance%20at%20the%202018%20Commonwealth%20Games%20further%20cemented%20her%20status%20as%20a%20shooting%20prodigy%2C%20where%20she%20won%20gold%20in%20the%20women%E2%80%99s%2010m%20air%20pistol%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBhaker%E2%80%99s%20journey%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20been%20without%20setbacks.%20At%20the%20Tokyo%202020%20Olympics%2C%20a%20pistol%20malfunction%20denied%20her%20a%20shot%20at%20a%20medal%20in%20the%20same%20event.%20However%2C%20she%20transformed%20that%20setback%20into%20a%20powerful%20comeback.%20Four%20years%20later%2C%20her%20outstanding%20performance%20in%20Paris%20has%20proved%20she%20is%20a%20force%20to%20be%20reckoned%20with.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20Bhaker%20approached%20the%20Paris%20Games%20with%20a%20balanced%20mind%2C%20taking%20online%20violin%20classes%20in%20the%20months%20leading%20up%20to%20them!%20This%20contrasted%20with%20her%20experience%20in%20Tokyo%2C%20where%20she%20had%20gone%20too%20deep%20into%20her%20shell.%20The%20lesson%20from%20Tokyo%2C%20she%20believes%2C%20was%20crucial.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20that%20lesson%20in%20my%20life%2C%20maybe%20I%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20here%20today%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20told%20%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99m%20glad%20that%20at%20such%20a%20young%20age%2C%20in%20my%20first%20Olympics%20experience%2C%20I%20learned%20the%20kind%20of%20things%20that%20people%20take%20years%20to%20learn%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC-CkS17TmXi%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC-CkS17TmXi%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC-CkS17TmXi%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20The%20Better%20India%20(%40thebetterindia)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20see%20her%20train%2C%20her%20discipline%2C%20blended%20with%20a%20hunger%20for%20excellence%2C%20would%20easily%20catch%20your%20attention.%20Bhaker%20has%20always%20credited%20her%20family%2C%20coaches%2C%20and%20support%20staff%20for%20being%20her%20support%20system.%20She%20says%20that%20their%20collective%20belief%20in%20her%20talent%20has%20propelled%20her%20to%20this%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20impact%20of%20her%20achievements%20is%20not%20confined%20to%20personal%20glory%20or%20her%20family%E2%80%99s%20pride.%20They%20have%20also%20inspired%20a%20new%20generation%20of%20Indian%20athletes%2C%20particularly%20young%20girls%2C%20to%20pursue%20their%20dreams%20in%20sports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Bhaker%20continues%20to%20compete%2C%20she%20remains%20a%20strong%20medal%20prospect%20in%20the%20upcoming%2025m%20pistol%20event%20at%20the%20Paris%20Olympics.%20Her%20historic%20accomplishments%20in%202024%20have%20already%20solidified%20her%20legacy%20in%20Indian%20sports%2C%20and%20she%20is%20poised%20to%20achieve%20even%20greater%20heights%20in%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722334117000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D359012%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Paris%20Olympics%202024%3A%20With%20another%20bronze%2C%20Manu%20Bhaker%20becomes%20the%20first%20Indian%20woman%20to%20win%20two%20shooting%20medals%20in%20a%20single%20Olympic%20edition.%20Her%20first%20was%20in%20the%20women's%2010m%20air%20pistol%20event%20and%20her%20second%20in%20the%2010m%20air%20pistol%20mixed%20team%20event.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Khushi%20Arora%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F359012%2Fmanu-bhaker-paris-olympics-shooting-bronze-medal-pistol-first-indian-woman-history-sarabjot-singh-haryana%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98I%20Fought%20Early%20Marriage%20For%20My%20Dreams%E2%80%99%3A%20UP%20Girl%20Uses%20Unique%20Art%20to%20Help%2020%20Others%20Find%20Freedom%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20main%20market%20in%20Risia%20block%2C%20Bahraich%20district%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20is%20bustling%20with%20activity.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20only%20big%20market%20for%20the%20entire%20block%2C%20there%20are%20several%20shops%20lining%20the%20narrow%20winding%20streets.%20While%20some%20sell%20groceries%2C%20vegetables%2C%20sweetmeats%20and%20readymade%20clothes%2C%20others%20offer%20tailoring%20and%20hair%20cutting%20services.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESqueezed%20among%20them%20is%20a%20small%20shop%20run%20by%20Rachna%20Kumari%2C%20a%20petite%20and%20soft-spoken%20young%20woman%20selling%20unique%20wheat%20stalk%20paintings%20handmade%20by%20her.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20surprisingly%2C%20this%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F318714%2Ftamil-nadu-engineer-turns-artist-paints-with-sunlight-vignesh%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20unconventional%20entrepreneurial%20choice%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20made%20the%2023-year-old%20the%20cynosure%20of%20all%20eyes%20for%20more%20reasons%20than%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201512px)%20100vw%2C%201512px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FIMG_0730_11zon-1722256363.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rachna%20with%20one%20of%20her%20creations.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FIMG_0730_11zon-1722256363.jpg%201512w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FIMG_0730_11zon-1722256363-225x300.jpg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FIMG_