a.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fca-final-1722243562.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Study%20buddies%20Nandini%20and%20Sachin%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fca-final-1722243562.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fca-final-1722243562-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fca-final-1722243562-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fca-final-1722243562-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fca-final-1722243562-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-358909%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EStudy%20buddies%20Nandini%20and%20Sachin%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20working%20on%20the%20feedback%2C%20they%20were%20better%20prepared.%20While%20the%20exams%20are%20usually%20held%20in%20May%20each%20year%2C%20in%202021%2C%20owing%20to%20COVID-19%2C%20they%20were%20postponed%20to%20July.%20Those%20two%20extra%20months%20served%20as%20a%20major%20boon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20duo%20didn%E2%80%99t%20let%20their%20guard%20down%20even%20with%20the%20extra%20time%E2%80%94they%20had%20their%20eyes%20on%20the%20prize.%20They%20did%20another%20revision%20and%20solved%20past%20papers%2C%20revision%20test%20papers%2C%20and%20mock%20test%20papers.%20For%20subjects%20they%20found%20difficult%2C%20like%20SFM%2C%20they%20spent%20extra%20time%2C%20which%20proved%20useful%20as%20they%20scored%20very%20well%20in%20it!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F348078%2Fdelhi-constable-than-singh-ki-pathshala-teaches-underprivileged-children-for-free%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efocused%20and%20studied%20hard%20%3C%2Fa%3Eright%20f