%3C%2Fvideo%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDayanand%20explains%20the%20methodology.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStep%201%3A%20Deflect%20%E2%80%93%20To%20prevent%20sewage%20from%20entering%20the%20lake%2C%20sluice%20gates%20were%20constructed%20at%20all%20inlets.%20A%20foreshore%20peripheral%20sewage%20interceptor%20carries%20the%20daily%20sewage%20to%20a%20sewage%20collection%20well%20which%20is%20attached%20to%20a%20STP%20(Sewage%20Treatment%20Plant)%2C%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStep%202%3A%20Drain.%20Once%20the%20sewage%20was%20deflected%2C%20the%20sewage%20water%20stored%20in%20the%20lake%20over%20years%20was%20drained%20through%20a%20sluice%20outlet%2C%20making%20the%20lake%20dry%20and%20free%20of%20dirt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStep%203%3A%20Desilt%3A%20Poor%20quality%20soil%20was%20removed%20and%20the%20lake%20was%20desilted%20completely.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStep%204%3A%20Deepen%3A%20To%20ensure%20rainwater%20storage%20and%20prevent%20flooding%2C%20the%20lake%20was%20deepened%20by%202.5%20metres.%20This%20was%20done%20after%20proper%20soil%20studies%20of%20the%20lake%20bed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F334084%2Fenvironment-hero-g-srikanth-vellore-tamil-nadu-braved-threats-to-grow-forest-inspiring%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elake%20was%20nursed%20back%20to%20health%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20one%20question%20still%20remained%20%E2%80%93%20How%20do%20you%20make%20it%20accessible%20for%20people%3F%20The%20civic%20group%20conducted%20a%20poll%20on%20their%20Facebook%20page%2C%20and%20based%20on%20the%20responses%2C%20these%20amenities%20were%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20walking%20path%2C%20play%20area%2C%20open%20air%20gym%2C%20amphitheatre%2C%20basketball%20court%2C%20and%20greenery%20were%20added%20to%20make%20the%20lake%20a%20recreational%20hub%20for%20the%20residents.%20Today%2C%20it%20is%20a%20symbol%20of%20energy%2